hadiths[50]{hadithnumber,text}:
1670,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''merey paas (shaane ki haddi) ya takhti laao, phir aap ney likhwaya padhi. : (لا يستوي القاعدون من المؤمنين) ''yani jihad sey bethey rehney waley momin (mujahideen key) barabar nahin ho saktey hain.'' na-bina Sahabi, Amr ibn Umme Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) aap key peechey they, unhoney puchha : kya merey liye ijazat hai? chunanche (aayat ka ( ye tukda nazil huwa : (غير أول الضرر) maazuron ke.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees ba-riwayat (Suleman Al Taimee an Abi Ishaaq) gharib hai, is hadees ko Shoba aur Sory ney bhi Abu-Is'haq sey riwayat kiya hai. 3- is bab mein ibne-Abbas , Jabir aur Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1671,"Eik aadmi jihad ki ijazat talab karney key liye Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat mein hazir huwa, aap ney puchha : ''kya tumharey maa baap ( zinda ( hain? usney kaha : haan , aap ney farmaya : ''un ki khidmat ki koshish mein lagey raho.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1672,Aayat kareema : « أطيعوا الله وأطيعوا الرسول وأولي الأمر منكم » ki tafseer mein kehtey hain : Abdullah bin Huzaafa bin Qais bin Adi Sahami ko Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney (akela) sariya bana kar bheja.
1673,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''agar log tanhai ka wo nuqsan jaan letey jo main janta hun to koi sawar raat mein tanha na chaley.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ibne-Umar ki hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1674,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''akela sawar shetan hai, do sawar bhi shetan hain aur teen sawar qafile waley hain.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Abdullah bin Amr ki hadees Hasan hai."
1675,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ladaai dhoka aur faraib ka naam hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Ali , Zaid bin Sabit , Aaisha ibne-Abbas , Asma binte Yazeed bin Sakan, Kaab bin Malik aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1676,"Main Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) key baghal mein tha ke un sey puchha gaya : Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney kitney ghazawaat kiye? kaha : unnis, mainey puchha : aap Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath kitney ghazawaat mein shareek rahey? kaha : satrah mein , mainey puchha : kon sa ghazwa pehley huwa tha? kaha : zaatul-ushair ya zaatul-ushaira. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1677,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney maqame Badr mein raat key waqt hamein munasib jagahon par mutayyan kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein abu-Ayyub sey bhi riwayat hai, ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey is hadees key barey mein puchha : to unhoney la-ilmi ka izhar kiya aur kaha : Muhammad bin Is-haq ka samaa (sun'na), ikrima sey Sabit hai, aur jab mainey Bukhari sey mulaqat ki thi to wo Muhammad bin Humed Al Raazi key barey mein achchhi raey rakhtey they, phir baad mein in ko zaeef qarar diya."
1678,"Mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko (ghazwa ehzaab mein) kuffar key lashkaron par bad dua kartey huye suna, aap ney in alfaz mein bad dua ki :(اللهم منزل الكتاب سريع الحساب اهزم الأحزاب اللهم اهزمهم وزلزلهم) ''kitab nazil karney aur jald hisab karney waley Allah ! kuffar key lashkaron ko shikast sey dochaar kar , in ko shikast dey aur unkey qadam ukhaad dey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi hadees marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
1679,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Makka mein dakhil huye to aap ka parcham safed tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Yahya bin Adam ki riwayat sey jantey hain aur Yahya Shareek sey riwayat kartey hain. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey is hadees key barey mein puchha : to unhoney kaha : Yahya bin Adam Shareek sey riwayat kartey hain, aur kaha : hum sey kaee logon ney (Shareek an Ammar an abi al Zuber an Jabir) ki sanad sey bayan kiya ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Makka mein dakhil huye aur us waqt aap key sar par kaalaa amama tha, Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : aur) mehfooz ( hadees yehi hai. 3- « الدهن » qabila bajeela ki eik shaakh hai, Ammar Dahni Muawiya dahni key betey hain, in ki kunniyat abu-Muaawia hai, wo koofa key rehney waley hain aur muhaddeseen key nazdik bharosemand hain."
1680,"Mujh ko Muhammad bin Qasim ney Bara bin Aazib Raziallahu anhuma key paas Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key jhandey key barey mein sawal karney key liye bheja , Bara ney kaha : ''aap ka jhandaa dhaari daar chakor aur kaalaa tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf ibne-Abi zyada ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 3- is bab mein Ali , Haris bin Hassan aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 4- Abu Yaqub Saqafi ka naam Is-haq bin Ibrahim hai, un sey Ubedullah bin Musa ney bhi riwayat ki hai."
1681,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka jhandaa kaalaa aur parcham safed tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ibne-Abbas ki ye riwayat is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai.
1682,"jinhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey suna , aap farma rahey they : ''agar raat main tum par dushman hamla karen to tum (حم لا ينصرون) kaho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- baaz logon ney isi tarah Sory ki riwayat key jaisi Abu-Is'haq Sabeei sey riwayat ki hai, aur Abu-Is'haq sey ye hadees ba-waste :(عن المهلب بن أبي صفرة an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) sey mursal tareeqe sey bhi aai hai. 2- is bab mein Salma bin Akwaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1683,"Mainey apni talwaar Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) ki talwaar ki tarah banai , aur Samura (Raziallahu anhu) ka khayal tha ke unhoney apni talwaar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key talwaar ki tarah banai thi aur aap ki talwaar qabila banu Haneefa ke tarz par banai gaee thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- Yahya bin Saeed Qataan ney Usman bin Saad Kaatib key silsiley mein kalam kiya hai aur hafizey mein unhen zaeef qarar diya hai."
1684,"Fateh Makka key saal jab Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam marruz-zohraan padhi. pahunchey aur hum ko dushman sey muqable ki khabar di to aap ney roza todney ka hukm diya, lihaza hum sab logon ney roza tod diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein umr sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1685,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam abu-Talha key ghodey par sawar ho gaey us ghodey ko (mandoob) kaha jata tha : koi ghabrahat ki baat nahin thi, is ghodey ko hamney chaal mein samandar paya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1686,"Madina mein ghabrahat ka mahol tha, chunanche Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamarey (mandoob) naami ghodey ko hum sey udhaar liya hamney koi ghabrahat nahin dekhi aur ghodey ko chaal mein hamney samandar paya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1687,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sab sey jari (nidar), sab sey sakhi , aur sab sey bahaadur they, eik raat Madina waley ghabra gaey, un logon ney koi aawaz suni , chunanche Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney talwaar latkaaey abu-Talha key eik nangi peeth waley ghodey par sawar ho kar logon key paas pahunchey aur farmaya : ''tum log fikr na karo, tum log fikr na karo''  Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main ney chaal mein ghodey ko samandar paya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai."
1688,"hum sey eik aadmi ney kaha : abu-Amaara ! kya aap log Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas sey farar ho gaey they? kaha : nahin, Allah ki qism ! Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney peeth nahin pheri , balke jald baaz logon ney peeth pheri thi, qabila Hawazin ney un par teeron sey hamla kar diya tha, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apney khachchar par sawar they, abu-Sufiyaan bin Haris bin Abdul-Muttalib khachar ki lagaam thaamey huye they padhi. , aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam farma rahey they : ''main Nabi hun, jhoota nahin hun, main Abdul-Muttalib ka beta hun. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Ali aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1689,"ghazwae-Hunain key din hamari soorate-haalat ye thi ke musalmanon ki dono jamaat peeth pherey hui thi, aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath so aadmi bhi nahin they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- isey hum Ubedullah ki riwayat sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
1690,"Fateh Makka key din Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Makka dakhil huye aur aap ki talwaar sone aur chaandi sey muzayyan (saji hui) thi, Raavi Talib kehtey hain : mainey Hud bin Abdullah sey chaandi key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : qabze ki gireh chaandi ki thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- Hud key dada ka naam Mazeeda Asri hai. 3- is bab mein Anas sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1691,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki talwaar key qabze ki gireh chaandi ki thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- isi tarah is hadees ko Hamaam , Qatada sey aur Qatada , Anas sey riwayat kartey hain, baaz logon ney Qatada key wastey sey , Saeed bin Abul-Hasan sey bhi riwayat ki hai, wo kehtey hain : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki talwaar key qabze ki gireh chaandi ki thi."
1692,"ghazwae-uhad key din Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key jism par do zirhen thin padhi. , aap chattan par chadhney lagey , lekin nahin chadh sakey , aap ney Talha bin Ubedullah ko apney nichey bithaya , phir aap un par chadh gaey yahan tak ke chattan par sidhey khadey ho gaey, Zuber kehtey hain : mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : '' Talha ney (apney amal sey jannat ( wajib kar li.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Muhammad bin Is-haq ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- is bab mein Safwan bin Umayya aur Saaib bin Yazeed Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1693,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Fateh Makka key saal Makka dakhil huye to aap key sar par khud tha, aap sey kaha gaya : ibne Khatal Kaba key pardon mein lipta huwa hai? aap ney farmaya : ''usey qatl kar do.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- hum mein sey aksar logon key nazdik Zohri sey Malik key ilawa kisi ney isey riwayat nahin ki hai."
1694,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ghodon ki peshani mein qiyamat tak khair (bhalai) bandhi hui hai, khair sey murad ajr aur ghanimat hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar , abu Saeed Khudri , Jareer , Abu-Hurera , Asma binte Yazeed , Mughira bin Shoba aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Imam Ahmed bin Hanbal kehtey hain, is hadees ka mafhoom ye hai ke jihad ka hukm har Imam key sath qiyamat tak baqi hai."
1695,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''surkh rang key ghodon mein barkat hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey is sanad sey sirf Sheban ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
1696,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' behtar ghodey wo hain jo kalay rang key hon , jinki peshani aur ooper ka hont safed ho, phir in key baad wo ghodey hain jin key chaaron pair aur peshani safed ho, agar ghoda kaley rang ka na ho to inhen sifaat ka surkh siyahi maael umda ghoda hai.''"
1697,usi maana ki usi jaisi hadees marvi (riwayat hui) hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai.
1698,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko ghodon mein sey « shikaal » ghoda napasand tha padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Shoba ney Abdullah bin Yazeed Khasami sey , basanad :(Abi Zaraa an abi Hurera an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) isi tarah ki hadees riwayat ki hai, abu-Zara'a Amr bin Jareer ka naam Harm hai."
1699,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney « تضمیر » kiye huye ghodon ki maqame hafiya sey saniyatil-wadaa tak daud karaai, in dono key darmiyan chhe mail ka fasla hai, aur jo « تضمیر » kiye huye nahin they in ko saniyatil-wadaa sey masjid bani Zuraiq tak ghud daud karaai, in dono key darmiyan eik mail ka fasla hai, ghud daud key muqabla mein main bhi shamil tha, chunanche mera ghoda mujhey ley kar eik deewar kood gaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Sory ki riwayat sey ye hadees sahih Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Jabir , Aaisha aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1700,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ne farmaya : ''muqabla sirf teer , oont aur ghodon mein jayez hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
1701,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Allah Taala key hukm key tabey (matehat) aur maamoor (lagaae hue) bandey they, aap ney hum ko dusron ki banisbat teen chizon ka khususi hukm diya : hum ko hukm diya padhi. ke puri tarah wuzu keren, sadqa na khaeyn aur ghodi par gadhaa na choden. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Sufiyan Sory ney Abu Jahzam sey riwayat kartey huye is hadees ki sanad yun bayan ki, (an Ubaidullah bin Abdullah bin Abbas an ibne-Abbas).3- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna ke Sory ki hadees ghair mehfooz hai, is mein Sory sey weham huwa hai, sahih wo riwayat hai jisey Ismail bin Aleh aur Abdul-Waaris bin Saeed ney Abu Zaham sey,  Abu Zaham Abdullah bin Ubedullah bin Abbas sey , aur Ubedullah ney ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat ki hai. 4- is bab mein Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai."
1702,"mainey Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : ''mujhey apney zaeefon aur kamzoron mein talash karo, isliye ke tum apney zaeefon aur kamzoron ki (duaaon ki barkat ki) wajeh sey rizq diye jatey ho aur tumhari madad ki jati hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1703,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' farishtey musafiron ki us jamaat key sath nahin rehtey hain jis mein kutta ya ghanti ho.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Umar, Aaisha, Umme-Habiba aur Umme-Salma (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1704,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney do lashkar rawana kiye, eik par Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ko aur doosrey par Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ko ameer muqarrar kya aur farmaya : ''jab jang ho to Ali ameer hongey padhi. '' , Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney eik qil'a Fateh kya aur is mein sey eik laundi ley li, Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ney mujh ko khat key sath Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas rawana kya, main Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya , aap ney khat padha to aap ka rang badal gaya, phir aap ney farmaya : '' us aadmi key barey main tumhara kya khayal hai jo Allah aur uskey Rasool sey mohabbat karta hai, aur Allah aur uskey Rasool bhi us sey mohabbat kartey hain? ''mainey arz kya : main Allah aur uskey Rasool key ghussey sey Allah ki panah maangta hun main to sirf qaasid hun, lihaza aap khamosh ho gaey padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isko sirf ahwas bin jawab ki riwayat sey jantey hain, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar sey bhi hadees marvi hai, padhi. - « يشي به » ka maana chughal khori hai."
1705,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum mein sey har aadmi nigehban hai aur apni ra'iyat key barey mein jawab deh hai, chunanche logon ka ameer unka nigehban hai aur wo apni riaayaa key barey mein jawab deh hai, isi tarah mard apney ghar walon ka nigehban hai aur unkey barey mein jawab deh hai, aurat apney shohar key ghar ki nigehban hai aur uskey barey mein jawab deh hai, ghulam apney Malik key maal ka nigehban hai aur uskey barey mein jawab deh hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Anas aur abu-Musa (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- abu-Musa ki hadees ghair mehfooz hai, aur Anas ki hadees bhi ghair mehfooz hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : usey Ibrahim bin Bashaar Ramadi ney ba-sanad (سفيان بن عيينة an بريد بن عبد الله بن أبي بردة an أبي بردة an أبي موسى an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) riwayat kya hai, is hadees ko kaee logon ney basanad ( سفيان an بريد an أبي بردة an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) mursal tariqa sey riwayat ki hai, magar ye mursal riwayat ziyada sahih hai. Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : Is-haq bin Ibrahim ney basanad (معاذ بن هشام an أبيه an قتادة an أنس an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) riwayat ki hai : beshak Allah Taala har nigehban sey puchega us chiz key barey mein jiski nigehbani key liye us ko rakha hai, Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna : ye riwayat ghair mehfooz hai, sahih wohi hai jo (عن معاذ بن هشام an أبيه an قتادة an الحسن an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) ki sanad sey mursal tareeqey sey aai hai."
1706,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko hajjatul-wadaa mein khutba detey huye suna, aap key jism par eik chadar thi jisey apni baghal key nichey sey lapetey huye they, (goya main) aap key bazu ka phadakta huwa gosht dekh rahi hun, mainey aap ko farmatey huye suna : ''logo! Allah sey daro, aur agar kaan kataa huwa Habshi ghulam bhi tumhara haakim bana diya jaey to uski baat mano aur uski itaat karo, jab tak wo tumharey liye kitabullah ko qaaim karey '' (yani kitabullah key muwaafiq hukm dey). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ( ye hadees (dusri sanadon sey bhi Umme Husain sey marvi hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera aur Arbaz bin Saariya Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1707,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tak maasiyat ka hukm na diya jaey musalman par samaa o taa-at lazim hai chahey wo pasand karey ya napasand kerey. aur agar usey maasiyat ka hukm diya jaey to na uskey liye sunna zaruri hai aur na itaat karna '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali , Imran bin Husain aur Hakam bin umr o Ghifaari (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1708,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney janweron ko baham (aapas mein) ladaney sey mana farmaya padhi. .
1709,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney janweron ko baham (aapas mein) ladaney sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is sanad mein Raavi ney ibne-Abbas ka zikr nahin kya hai, 2- kaha jata hai, Qutba ki) agli ( hadees sey ye hadees ziyada sahih hai, is hadees ko Shurek ney b-tareeq (مجاهد an ابن عباس an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) isi tarah riwayat kya hai aur is mein abu-Yahya ka zikr nahin kya hai 2- aur abu-Muaawia ney isko b-tareeq (الأعمش an مجاهد an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) isi tarah riwayat kya hai, abu-Yahya sey murad abu-Yahya Qataat koofi hain, kaha jata hai unka naam Zazaan hai, 4- is bab mein Talha , Jabir , abu-Saeed aur Ikrash bin Zuwwab (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1710,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney chehrey par maarney aur usey daaghney sey mana farmaya padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1711,"eik lashkar mein mujhey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key samney pesh kya gaya, main chaudah saal ka tha, to aap ney mujhey (jihad mein ladney key liye) qubul nahin kya, phir mujhey aap key samney aainda saal eik lashkar mein pesh kya gaya aur main pandarah saal ka tha, to aap ney mujhey (lashkar mein) qubul kar liya, Nafey kehtey hain ke mainey is hadees ko umr bin abdul-Azeez sey bayan kya to unhoney kaha : chhotey aur badey key darmiyan yehi had hai, phir unhoney farman jari kya ke jo pandarah saal ka ho jaey usey maale-ghanimat sey hissa diya jaey."
1712,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Sahaba key bech khadey ho kar un sey bayan kya : '' Allah ki raah mein jihad karna aur Allah par eman lana sab sey afzal amal hai'' padhi. , ( ye sun kar) eik aadmi khada huwa aur arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! aap ka kya khayal hai agar main Allah ki raah mein shaheed ho jaaun, to kya merey gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey? Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''haan agar tum Allah ki raah mein shaheed ho gaey is haal mein ke tum sabr karney waley, sawab ki ummid rakhney waley ho, aagey badhney waley ho, peechey mudney waley na ho'', phir aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum ney kaisey kaha hai? '' arz kya : aap ka kya khayal hai agar main Allah ki raah mein shaheed ho jaaun to kya merey gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey? Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''haan agar tum sabr karney waley, sawab ki ummid rakhney waley ho aur aagey badhney waley ho peechey mudney waley na ho, siwaye qarz key, ye mujh sey Jibreel ney ( abhi ( kaha hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- baaz logon ney ye hadees basanad (سعيد المقبري an أبي هريرة an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) isi tarah riwayat ki hai, Yahya bin Saeed Ansari aur kaee logon ney us ko basanad (سعيد المقبري an عبد الله ابن أبي قتادة an أبيه an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) sey riwayat ki hai, ye riwayat Saeed Maqbari ki riwayat sey jo b-wasta Abu-Hurera aai hai, ziyada sahih hai, 4- is bab mein Anas , Muhammad bin Jahash aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1713,"Uhud key din Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey zakhmon ki shikayat ki gaee padhi. , aap ney farmaya : '' qabr khodo aur usey kushada aur achi banao , eik qabr mein do ya teen aadmiyon ko dafn karo, aur jisey ziyada Quran yad ho usey ( qibley ki taraf ( aagey karo '' , Hisham bin Aamir kehtey hain : merey walid bhi wafat paey they, chunanche in ko unkey do sathiyon par muqaddam ( yani qibley ki taraf aagey ( kya gaya ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Sufiyan Sory aur doosrey logon ney is hadees ko basanad (أيوب an حميد بن هلال an هشام بن عامر) riwayat kya hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein khubaab, Jabir aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1714,"jab Badr key din qaidiyon ko laya gaya to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' unkey barey main tum log kya kehtey ho '' , phir Raavi ney is hadees main eik taweel qissa bayan kya padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- abu-Ubaida ney apney baap sey nahin suna hai, 3- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey badh kar kisi ko nahin dekha jo apney sathiyon sey ziyada mashwara leta ho padhi. , 4- is hadees mein Umar, abu-Ayyub, Anas aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1715,"mushrekin ney eik mushrik ki laash ko khareedna chaha to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney isey bechney sey inkar kar diya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- hum isey sirf Hakam ki riwayat sey jantey hain, isko hujjaaj bin irtaat ney bhi Hakam sey riwayat kya hai, 3- Ahmed bin Hanbal kehtey hain : ibne-Abi Leila ki hadees qabile-hujjat nahin hai, 4- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : ibne-Abi Leila Sadooq hain lekin hum ko un ki sahih hadisein un ki zaeef hadeeson sey pehchan nahin paatey , main un sey kuch nahin riwayat karta hun, ibne-Abi Leila Sadooq hain faqeeh hain, lekin kabhi-kabhi un sey sanadon mein weham ho jata hai, 5- Sufiyan Sory kehtey hain : hamarey fuqaha ibne-Abi Leila aur Abdullah bin Shabarma hain."
1716,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hum ko eik sariya mein rawana kya, (phir hum) log ladaai sey bhag khadey huye, Madina aaye to sharam ki wajeh sey chup gaey aur hamney kaha : halak ho gaey, phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat mein hazir huye aur arz kya : Allah key Rasool! hum bhagodey hain, aap ney farmaya : ''balke tum log peechey hat kar hamla karney waley ho aur main tumhara pusht-panah hun''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, hum isey sirf Yazeed bin abi Ziyad ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 2- « فحاص الناس حيصة » ka maana ye hai ke log ladaai sey farar ho gaey, 3- aur (بل أنتم العكارون) isko kehtey hain : jo farar ho kar apney Imam ( کمانڈر ( key paas aa jaey taake wo uski madad karey na ke ladaai sey farar honey ka irada rakhta ho."
1717,"Uhud key din meri phuphi merey baap ko ley kar ayen taake unhen hamarey qabristaan mein dafn karen, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key eik manadi ney pukara : maqtulon ko unki qatl gaahon mein lota do ( dafn karo) padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. - aur Nabih Suqa hain."
1718,jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ghazwa tabuk sey wapis aaye to log aap key istaqbal key liye saniya al-Wadaa tak nikley : main bhi logon key sath nikla halanke main kam umr tha . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1719,"Aswad key qabila bani Nazir key amwaal un mein sey they jisey Allah Taala ney apney Rasool Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko bator « Fai  ata kya tha, uskey liye musalmanon ney na to ghodey daudaaey they aur na hi oont, ye purey ka pura maal khalis Allah key Rasool Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key liye tha, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apney ghar walon key liye is mein sey eik saal ka kharch alag kar letey , phir jo baqi bachta usey jihad ki tayyari key liye ghodon aur hathiyaron mein kharch kartey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Sufiyan bin Uena ney is hadees ko Maamar key wastey sey ibne-Shahab sey riwayat kya hai."
